@startuml
title Object lifecycle: Student Discord credential
[*] --> NotLinked
NotLinked --> Linked : OAuth callback stores identity and token
Linked --> Refreshed : stored refresh token is exchanged
Refreshed --> Linked : new access token persisted
Linked --> Expired : token expires before refresh
Expired --> Refreshed : refresh succeeds
Expired --> NotLinked : refresh fails and teacher re-authorizes later
Linked --> [*]
@enduml
